<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>MCW-MUG E-Mail List 
</TITLE></HEAD>
<BODY><H1>MCW-MUG E-Mail List
</H1>
<P>The MCW Macintosh Users Group (mcw-mug) is available to all
interested faculty, students, and staff, via electronic mail  (e-mail). 
This group will keep you abreast of the latest  information on computer
hardware, software, and applications.   You can also ask questions and
request help from your fellow  Mac users on campus.    All user group
activities are conducted over e-mail; there is no  cost to join!  If you
have an e-mail account and want your name  added to this electronic
mailing list, send a message to:<P>

<A HREF="mailto:listproc@post.its.mcw.edu">listproc@post.its.mcw.edu</A><P>

The body of your message must contain:  <B>subscribe mcw-mug</B><P>

Note, if you want to discontinue membership in the group, e-mail 
the same address and include the following in the body of your  message:
  unsubscribe mcw-mug  This user group is being coordinated by Dr. Gary
Barnas of the  Division of General Internal Medicine. If you have any
further  questions or desire additional information please contact him 
at 257-6323 or send e-mail to: <A HREF="mailto:barnas@post.its.mcw.edu">barnas</A>.
<HR>
<ADDRESS>Last edited: 4/28/95</ADDRESS> 
<ADDRESS><A HREF="http://www.intmed.mcw.edu/mcw-mug/mcw-mug.html">Return to MCW-MUG HomePage</A></ADDRESS></BODY>
</HTML>

