<h2 align=center><a name="title">The National Consumer Complaint Center <sup><font size=2>TM</font></sup></a></h2>
<hr>
<p><font size=5>S</font>ponsored by <a href="http://www.alexanderlaw.com/alexanderlaw/index.html">The Alexander Law Firm</a>, <strong>The National Consumer Complaint Center</strong> is offered to provide a method of 
promptly communicating consumer complaints to agencies that are interested in investigating and taking action for consumers. 
<font color="#FF0000">Bookmark</font> this page to your list of sites so you can quickly find it if you need to make a report. </p>
<p><font size=5>S</font>elect the category which best fits your complaint:</p>
<p align=center><a href="http://seamless.com/cgi-bin/imagemap/talf/nccc/nccc.map"><img src="nccc3.gif" alt=" " align=bottom border=0 width=460 height=264 ISMAP></a> </p>
<ul>
<li><a href="cb-car.html"><font size=2>Automobiles, Trucks, Motorcycles</font></a><font size=2> </font></li>
<li><a href="cb-food.html"><font size=2>Food, Drugs, Cosmetics, Medical Devices, Radiation-emitting Electronic Products, Veterinary Drugs and Feeds</font></a><font size=2> </font></li>
<li><a href="cb-pest.html"><font size=2>Pesticides, Herbicides, Related Chemicals, Air and Water Pollution</font></a><font size=2> </font></li>
<li><a href="cb-house.html"><font size=2>Consumer Products, Hazardous Household Products, Appliances, and Toys</font></a><font size=2> </font></li>
<li><a href="cb-poul.html"><font size=2>Meat and Poultry Products</font></a><font size=2> </font></li>
<li><a href="cb-ftc.html"><font size=2>Internet Fraud, False Advertising and Breached Warranties</font></a><font size=2> </font></li>
<li><a href="cb-comp.html"><font size=2>Computers, Printers, Modems and Related High Tech Products</font></a> </li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h4>Press the &quot;back arrow&quot; to return to the previous page.</h4>
<h4>Press <a href="http://seamless.com/alexanderlaw/txt/intro.html">here</a> to return to The Consumer Law Page.</h4>
<h4>Press <a href="http://www.alexanderlaw.com/alexanderlaw/index.html">here</a> to return to The Alexander Law Firm Homepage.</h4>
