<h2><a href="index.html">The Alexander Law Firm</a>: Guest Book and Reader Feedback Form</h2>
<form action="http://seamless.com/cgi-bin/tsw-talfg-new.pl" method="POST">
<hr>
<p><font size=5>W</font>elcome to THE ALEXANDER LAW FIRM site guest book and reader feedback form. Use this form to send messages to 
us, to suggest links, to request more information about our site, and to order a free copy of our firm's information packet. Should 
your client software not support forms, you may contact us by e-mailing us at <a href="mailto:access@alexanderlaw.com">access@alexanderlaw.com</a>.</p>
<p><font size=5>Y</font>ou may also wish to check out our new <a href="ques.html">&quot;How to Become an Alexander Law Firm Client&quot;</a> page, which allows you to post 
directly to our site any question you may have about a potential case.</p>
<p><font size=5>H</font>ow did you <strong>first</strong> find out about this site? </p>
