<option value="commercial">From another commercial homepage</option>
<option value="yellow-pages">From an Internet "Yellow Pages" listing</option>
<option value="search">From a WWW search engine (e.g. Lycos, etc.)</option>
<option value="USENET">From a posting on USENET</option>
<option value="list">From a mailing list</option>
<option value="flyer">From a flyer I received</option>
