<h2 align="center">Introduction</h2>

<hr>

<p><font size="5">O</font>ur sincere appreciation to Point Survey
for including this site in their Top 5% of the Web [45/50 for
content] and to McKinley's Magellan Internet Directory for the
award of Three Stars. </p>

<p><font size="5">P</font>lease <font color="#FF0000">BOOKMARK</font>
this site for future reference. </p>

<p><font size="5">T</font>he Consumer Law Page is regularly
updated. Sign our <a
href="http://seamless.com/alexanderlaw/guestb.html">guest book</a>
and we will notify you of updates with a very brief note. We are
very interested in your comments, questions and suggestions on
how to improve and better serve you. Our resources section has
been expanded greatly in response to your recommendations. Please
tell us what has been most helpful to you, what you would like to
see or share a hotsite with us that we should post to our
directory. </p>

<p><font size="5">T</font>his page is sponsored by <a
href="http://seamless.com/alexanderlaw/index.html">The Alexander
Law Firm</a>, a law firm leading the legal profession in serving
the public, consumers and small businesses, individually and in
class actions, in cases in which corporate abuse, fraud,
defective products and toxic chemicals has caused personal
injuries or damage to property. <font color="#000080">In October,
1996 we are proud to have received <strong>over 630,000 hits</strong>
to our page, which we update regularly. Thank you for your
positive response.</font> </p>

<hr>

<p><a href="article/index.html"><img src="articles.gif" alt=" "
align="left" hspace="10" width="116" height="66"></a><font
size="5">C</font>ollected here are some excellent <a
href="article/index.html">articles</a> on various topics of
interest to consumers, and to the Plaintiff's Bar. Examples of
topics covered include <strong>products liability</strong> and <strong>toxic
torts</strong>. <font size="1">[970204]</font><font size="3"> <br
clear="all">
</font></p>

