                class actions are ineffective because of
                prevailing individual issues involving an
                investor's account. If you've been ripped off,
                scammed, or misled in your investing efforts by
                brokers who either should have known better or
                were taking advantage of you, NCII is the place
                to turn. The Investor's Rights section guides you
                in solving your investment problems and offers an
                excellent overview of arbitration, which is
                mandated by most brokerage contracts. This is a
                substantial, worthwhile and extremely valuable
                site, which <a href="http://consumerlawpage.com">The
