<input type=text size=5 maxlength=256 name="state"> State<br>
<input type=text size=10 maxlength=256 name="zip"> Zip<br>
<input type=text size=20 maxlength=256 name="dayphone"> Day Telephone<br>
<input type=text size=20 maxlength=256 name="evetelephone"> Evening Telephone<br>
<input type=text size=20 maxlength=256 name="fax"> Fax<br>
<input type=text size=20 maxlength=256 name="email"> Email<br>
<input type=text size=35 maxlength=256 name="occupation"> Occupations of Adopting Parents<br>
<input type=text size=35 maxlength=256 name="childname"> Name of Adopted Child<br>
<input type=text size=20 maxlength=256 name="birth"> Date of Birth of Child<br>
<input type=text size=20 maxlength=256 name="adoptiondate"> Date of Adoption<br>
<input type=text size=20 maxlength=256 name="county"> County of Adoption<br>
<input type=text size=20 maxlength=256 name="orderdate"> Date Adoption Order or Decree Entered<br>
<input type=text size=20 maxlength=256 name="authorizing"> County Authorizing Adoption<br>
<input type=text size=20 maxlength=256 name="type"> Type of Child Requested<br>
<input type=text size=20 maxlength=256 name="unacceptable"> Type of Child That Was Unacceptable</p>
<p>What were you told in writing about this child's family background,<br>
medical history, or placement history?</p>
