Affairs; Vice-Chair, Commission on Mandatory Malpractice Insurance for California Attorneys, 1986-1987; President, Santa 
Clara County Bar Association, 1984; President, Santa Clara County Bar Foundation, 1984; Member, Committee on 
Professional Ethics, The State Bar of California, 1977-1980; Santa Clara County Bar Association: Trustee 1979-1980, 1982- 
1983; Lawyers Committee on Women, 1976-; Client Relations and Professional Ethics Committee, 1977-1980; Executive 
Committee, Consumer Law Section, 1977-1978; Long Range Planning, 1979-1980; Judiciary Committee, 1979; Executive 
