<h3><a name="radio">NATIONAL RADIO BROADCASTING</a></h3>
<p>Legal Commentator for &quot;Marketplace,&quot; a nationally broadcast business news program, heard on American Public Radio in 100 
cities throughout the United States, 1989-1990. </p>
<hr>
