<head>
<title>Consumer Product Incident Report</title>
<meta name="GENERATOR" content="Microsoft FrontPage 1.1">
</head>

<body link="#0000FF" vlink="#FF4500">
<h2 align=center p>Consumer Product Incident Report </h2>
<hr>
<p>By filling out the form below and then submitting it, you can report any injury or death involving consumer products to the 
Consumer Product Safety Commission (CPSC). The CPSC may contact you by mail or by telephone for further details or to 
confirm the information you sent. Please provide as much information as possible. You may also report an incident by calling 
toll-free at 1-800-638-8095. </p>
<p>When filling out the form, use the &lt;TAB&gt; key or your mouse to go to the next data area. Use the scroll bar to scroll down the 
form. </p>
<p>(<em>Please note that the information submitted via this form will also be archived by the </em><a href="cb-intro.html"><em>Center</em></a><em> for the purpose of 
monitoring consumer complaints.</em>)</p>
<form action="http://seamless.com/cgi-bin/tsw-talf-cb-cpsc.pl" method="POST">
<p>Your name: <input type=text size=40 maxlength=256 name="name"> </p>
<p>Your address: <input type=text size=40 maxlength=256 name="address"> </p>
<p>City: <input type=text size=25 maxlength=256 name="city"> </p>
<p>State: <input type=text size=2 maxlength=256 name="state"> </p>
<p>Zip code: <input type=text size=10 maxlength=256 name="zip"> </p>
<p>Your telephone: <input type=text size=20 maxlength=256 name="telephone"> </p>
<p>Your email address: <input type=text size=20 maxlength=256 name="email"></p>
<p>Name of victim (if different from above): <input type=text size=40 maxlength=256 name="vname"> </p>
<p>Victim address: <input type=text size=40 maxlength=256 name="vaddress"> </p>
<p>City: <input type=text size=25 maxlength=256 name="vcity"> </p>
<p>State: <input type=text size=2 maxlength=256 name="vstate"> </p>
<p>Zip code: <input type=text size=10 maxlength=256 name="vzip"> </p>
<p>Victim day telephone: <input type=text size=20 maxlength=256 name="vdtelephone"> </p>
<p>Victim evening telephone: <input type=text size=20 maxlength=256 name="vetelephone"> </p>
<p>Describe the incident or hazard, including description of injuries<br>
<textarea name="incident" rows=20 cols=60></textarea> </p>
<p>Victim's Age: <input type=text size=9 maxlength=256 name="vage"> </p>
<p>Victim's sex<br>
<input type=radio name="sex" value="Female">Female<br>
<input type=radio name="sex" value="Male">Male </p>
<p>Date of Incident: <input type=text size=8 maxlength=256 name="idate"> </p>
<p>Describe product involved:<br>
<input type=text size=60 maxlength=256 name="product"> </p>
<p>Product Brand Name/Manufacturer:<br>
<input type=text size=60 maxlength=256 name="brand"> </p>
<p>Is product involved still available?<br>
<input type=radio name="product_available" value="Yes">Yes<br>
<input type=radio name="product_available" value="No">No </p>
<p>Product model and serial number:<br>
<input type=text size=60 maxlength=256 name="model_serial_no" BR> </p>
<p>When was the product purchased? <input type=text size=20 maxlength=256 name="purchased" BR> </p>
<p><input type=submit value="Send to CPSC"> <input type=reset value="Clear Form"> </p>
</form>
