<p><strong>Brief description of what happened =<br>
<textarea name="sequence" rows=5 cols=50></textarea> </strong></p>
<p><strong><input type=text size=20 maxlength=90 name="city"> = City and state where the incident occurred</strong></p>
<p><strong><input type=text size=20 maxlength=90 name="brand"> = Manufacturer, seller or company responsible for</strong></p>
<p><strong>Have you kept any printed materials, containers, etc. =<input type=radio name="kept" value="yes">Yes <input type=radio name="kept" value="no">No.</strong></p>
<p><strong>Contact information for any state or local personnel who investigated the incident =<br>
<textarea name="contact" rows=5 cols=50></textarea> </strong></p>
