<p><a href="fight.html"><font size="3"><img src="fight.gif"
alt=" " align="left" hspace="10" width="116" height="66"></font></a><font
size="5">F</font><font size="3">iling a consumer complaint with a
local county consumer agency or the Better Business Bureau, and
in some cases a Small Claims Court lawsuit, can be the best way
to put a stop to consumer abuse by a local wrongdoer. In other
cases, in which consumers are abused by major corporations, only
the power of a consumer class action can correct misdeeds. </font></p>

