programs and laws (2/94). </p>
<p>Smithsonian Institution Photographs: Archive of photographs from the Smithsonian's Office of Printing &amp; Photographic 
Services, available as electronic images. Path: ftp photo1.si.edu/ user:anonymous/password:e-mail address (2/94). </p>
