<h4><font color="#FF0000">Press </font><a href="http://consumerlawpage.com/nographics/article/breast.shtml"><font color="#FF0000">here</font></a><font color="#FF0000"> for a &quot;no-graphics&quot; version of this page</font></h4>
<p><a href="index.html#toxic"><img src="../workers.gif" alt="[Workers Injured by Toxics]" align=bottom border=0 width=142 height=33></a> <a href="lenses.shtml"><img src="../lenses.gif" alt=" [Bausch &amp; Lomb Contact Lenses Class Action] " align=bottom border=0 width=142 height=33></a> <a href="http://seamless.com/alexanderlaw/nccc/cb-intro.html"><img src="../sm-nccc.gif" alt=" [National Consumer Complaint Center] " align=bottom border=0 width=142 height=33></a> <a href="../reserved.html"><img src="../reserved.gif" alt=" [Settlement Reached - GM Pickup Truck] " align=bottom border=0 width=142 height=33></a> 
