<a href="howhire.shtml"><img src="../finding.gif" alt=" [Finding the Right Lawyer]" align=bottom border=0 width=142 height=33></a> <a href="fraud/fraud.shtml"><img src="../protect.gif" alt=" [Protect Yourself from Fraud] " align=bottom border=0 width=142 height=33></a> <a href="nolan.shtml"><img src="../lawyer.gif" alt=" [Lawyer of the Month] " align=bottom border=0 width=142 height=33></a> <a href="ibm.shtml"><img src="../ibm.gif" alt="[IBM Employees: Cancer Investigation]" align=bottom border=0 width=142 height=33></a> 
